		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I own a pirate nes console and a pirate nes cartridge (both of them are 60 pin). Recently I have translated a nes game to my native language and I can play it on my computer without any trouble but I really want to play it on my nes console! How can I do it? Can someone help me?
<br />Thanks in advance

		

