		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What kind of cartridge is it, and have you taken it apart?  You'll want one that uses normal memory chips, a lot of pirate carts that I've seen use glop-tops and you can't rewire anything (not easily) since there is no removable chip (just a blob of epoxy).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


